summary: just for the record, so i can say i predicted it if it’s true, here is what i think the post credits scene of captain marvel...
body:
just for the record, so i can say i predicted it if it’s true, here is what i think the post credits scene of captain marvel will be:

nick fury is sitting in his office in shield. maybe carol, coulson or someone else is there with him. suddenly, he hears a bit of a commotion outside, but before he has time to check what is happening a figure appears in front of him. who? ant-man. scott lang, who having realised something bad happened to his friends, sought out a time vortex as a means to escape the quantum realm and ended up in the ‘90s, where he made a beeline for shield headquarters and nick fury. he explains everything to him to the best of his ability and has to spend the next 20 years not interfering in his own life or the lives of his loved ones until the day comes when he can finally understand what is going on.

Captain Marvel Prelude #1

Publisher: Marvel Comics
(W) Will Pilgrim (A) Andrea Di Vito

Before CAROL DANVERS takes flight in 2019’s first Marvel Studios film, immerse yourself in this all-new adventure! Spinning out of the mysterious events of Avengers: Infinity War, NICK FURY and MARIA HILL set off on life-or-death missions that lead directly to the appearance of CAPTAIN MARVEL!

In Shops: Nov 14, 2018
